If FlipStreamScreenGrabber is enabled, it will start buffering screenshots. As a result, its output will begin from (frames * fps) seconds before the delay_sec. For example, if frames = 24, fps = 8, and delay_sec = 8.0, it will start from 5 seconds.

This workflow depends on additional custom nodes:
ComfyUI Impact Pack
LoRA Tag Loader for ComfyUI
ComfyUI-AnimateDiff-Evolved
ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite
ComfyUI-Inspyrenet-Rembg
ComfyUI-DepthAnythingV2
ComfyUI-Frame-Interpolation

from https://huggingface.co/tianweiy/DMD2/tree/main
